{"tid":1592530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"想問下啲人去乜撚野同林奠對話？？？","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:23:16.000Z","uid":85390,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"797a67dc90a59da0ff8a03689bdb6ddfcd4c9c52","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭咁多日以來講埋哂啲涼薄撚屌嘅廢話，你地覺得去同佢對話會撚到佢？ 再同我地認錯改善？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚天真啦，呢個對話show 係比佢做比大眾睇，話比國際社會知佢有同正反立場嘅人對話，做哂交代啦！<br />\n<br />\n你班傻鳩去幫佢做勢同埋令到對話認受性增加，屌你老味。如果你仲係同我地同一陣線就咪撚去，由佢小圈子同啲藍絲對話飽佢，反正都影響唔到我地。<br />\n<br />\n若果有自己友去同佢對話，我（代表自己）實割蓆，因為去嘅人真係好撚蠢，點對得住受傷流血犧牲嘅手足？<br />\n<br />\n我地係要佢直接答應 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38aaf0c45cd894bd19f7770eafee3c76b4a069d9","tid":1592530,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"1e132a945a5ff69bcd7b9866f65c6fcb18560875","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我被抽中出席林鄭月娥個對話會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到呢個post 啲正評做乜撚野？<br />\n大家都好想同林奠傾下計？談談心？<br />\n嬲到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f8747aed3b18b23cdbf6d354d689661f33492d","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lih.kg/1592003\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flih.kg%2F1592003&h=cc07fa14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己睇下，仲同林奠對話？？？ <br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"d23c3d387d31df2eb5fe52f3f8fc55d0b831d564","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40f8747aed3b18b23cdbf6d354d689661f33492d","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lih.kg/1592003\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flih.kg%2F1592003&h=cc07fa14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己睇下，仲同林奠對話？？？ <br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNds8Yd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNds8Yd.jpg&h=f45f3fa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fcf34134e9438a5e919079a677140d76a4f2558","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"你地即管負皮，但比唔比到一個去嘅理由？？？"},{"pid":"0842b9722f4dbef170797a34150a54d0b5c4762e","tid":1592530,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"報名滿晒額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684a4e0fe669ffe412a522a070eadc04197c3b8e","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 ， 好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554fee6e231bb4856671163bf242ea1c7a9c92cb","tid":1592530,"uid":85390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0842b9722f4dbef170797a34150a54d0b5c4762e","tid":1592530,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"